RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_SETTLEMENTS__SPLM.CONTRACT_REF_NO = OLTBS_SETTLEMENTS__CONIS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_SETTLEMENTS__SPLM.BASIS_AMOUNT_TAG = OLTBS_SETTLEMENTS__CONIS.BASIS_AMOUNT_TAG AND OLTBS_SETTLEMENTS__SPLM.EVENT_SEQ_NO = OLTBS_SETTLEMENTS__CONIS.EVENT_SEQ_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, CUSTOMER_NAME1,'Y' AS DFLT_STL FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND INSTR('IE', CCY_EUR_TYPE) > 0 AND CCY_CODE <> ?
SELECT FIELD_NAME, FIELD_DESC FROM OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE WHERE MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'SRCD' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE.FIELD_NAME, OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE.FIELD_DESC FROM OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE WHERE MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'ISBC'
SELECT OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE.FIELD_NAME, OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE.FIELD_DESC FROM OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE WHERE MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'ISIC'
SELECT FIELD_NAME, FIELD_DESC FROM OLTM_STATIC_MAINTENANCE WHERE MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'SRCD' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, AC_GL_DESC FROM (SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, AC_GL_DESC,AC_OR_GL FROM (SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, AC_GL_DESC,AC_OR_GL FROM OLVWS_ALL_ACCOUNTS WHERE NVL(BRANCH_CODE, ?) = ? AND Cust_No = Nvl(?, Cust_No) AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> '5' AND (NVL(AC_GL_CCY, ?) = ? OR (NVL(AC_GL_CCY, ?) = ?)) UNION SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, AC_GL_DESC,AC_OR_GL FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE NVL(BRANCH_CODE, ?) = ? AND Cust_No = Nvl(?, Cust_No) AND AC_OR_GL = 'A' AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> '5' AND (NVL(AC_GL_CCY, ?) = ? OR (NVL(AC_GL_CCY, ?) = ?)) AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A') UNION SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, AC_GL_DESC,AC_OR_GL FROM (SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, AC_GL_DESC,AC_OR_GL FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT WHERE ((BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL AND branch_code = nvl(?, branch_code)) OR (BRANCH_CODE IS NULL AND NVL(BRANCH_CODE, NVL(?, '***')) = NVL(?, '***'))) AND ((Cust_No = Nvl(?, Cust_No) AND Ac_Or_Gl = 'A') OR Ac_Or_Gl <> 'A') AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY AC_OR_GL, AC_GL_NO)) a WHERE (A.AC_OR_GL = 'G' OR (A.AC_OR_GL = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE A.AC_GL_NO = X.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?))) ORDER BY AC_GL_NO
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT WHERE BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL OR (BRANCH_CODE IS NULL AND NVL(BRANCH_CODE, NVL(?, '***')) = NVL(?, '***')) AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' ORDER BY AC_OR_GL, AC_GL_NO

SELECT Settlement_Seq_No Seq_No, Ssi_Mnemonic, Branch, Decode(?, 'P', Pay_Account, 'R', Recv_Account) Account, Currency, Decode(?, 'P', Instr_Type_Pay, 'R', Instr_Type_Rec) AS Instr_Type, 'Y' AS DFLT_STL FROM Oltms_Instr WHERE Decode(Counterparty, 'ALL', ?, Counterparty) = ? AND Decode(Branch, 'ALL', ?, Branch) = ? AND Decode(Module, 'AL', ?, Module) = ? AND Decode(Product_Code, 'ALL', ?, Product_Code) = ? AND Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' and EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (X.AC_GL_NO = PAY_ACCOUNT OR X.AC_GL_NO = RECV_ACCOUNT) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)

SELECT BIC_CODE, RELATIONSHIP, BANK_NAME FROM (SELECT B.BIC_CODE BIC_CODE ,DECODE(B.RELATIONSHIP,'K','Keys','M','Mail','No') RELATIONSHIP,B.BANK_NAME BANK_NAME FROM ISTMS_BIC_DIRECTORY B WHERE B.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' UNION SELECT (A.NETWORK_PREFIX||A.NETWORK_CODE||B.CLEARING_CODE) BIC_CODE,'' RELATIONSHIP,B.BANK_NAME BANK_NAME FROM ISTMS_NETWORK_CODE A,ISTMS_CLEARING_CODE B WHERE B.NETWORK_CODE = A.NETWORK_CODE AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y') WHERE 1=1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT BIC_CODE,DECODE(RELATIONSHIP,'K','Keys','M','Mail','No') RELATIONSHIP, BANK_NAME FROM ISTMS_BIC_DIRECTORY WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' ORDER BY BIC_CODE
SELECT BANK_CODE, BANK_NAME FROM ISVWS_LOCAL_BANK_DIRECTORY WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STATUS = 'A'
